description: Lists the notification hubs associated with a namespace.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

value.description: Result of the List NotificationHub operation.

nextlink.description: Link to the next set of results. Not empty if Value contains incomplete list of NotificationHub
